description: Kaneki Kyouko is a student of 9 Grade Class 3 in 1998, attendance number 9. She sits in classroom in front of Takako Sugiura and is seen to be a good friend of Matsui Aki. She is one of the eight "Deaths of August", being killed by Kazami Tomohiko when she was trying to escape with Matsui.
name: Kaneki Kyouko
